snippet: Dara Torres, who turns 45 next month, is attempting another comeback in pursuit of making her sixth Olympic swim team this summer.
lead_paragraph: Dara Torres, who turns 45 next month, is attempting another comeback in pursuit of making her sixth Olympic swim team this summer.
